{{quote|'''''New options for fighters, rangers, rogues, and warlords.'''

''Martial Power is the first of a line of player-friendly supplements offering hundreds of new options for D&D characters. This tome focuses on the martial heroes: characters that rely on their combat talents and keen wits for survival.''}}

This book provides new archetypal builds for the [[fighter]], [[ranger]], [[rogue]], and [[warlord]] classes, including new character powers, feats, [[:Category:Paragon paths|paragon paths]], and epic destinies.
